            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EEzekiel%2042%3A1-43%3A27%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_42_1%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EEzekiel%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E42%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3ERooms%20for%20the%20Priests%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20man%20led%20me%20out%20of%20the%20Temple%20courtyard%20by%20way%20of%20the%20north%20gateway.%20We%20entered%20the%20outer%20courtyard%20and%20came%20to%20a%20group%20of%20rooms%20against%20the%20north%20wall%20of%20the%20inner%20courtyard.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_42_2%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20structure%2C%20whose%20entrance%20opened%20toward%20the%20north%2C%20was%20175%26%23xA0%3Bfeet%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E42%3A2a%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3E100%26%23xA0%3Bcubits%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5B53%26%23xA0%3Bmeters%5D%3B%20also%20in%2042%3A8.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20long%20and%2087%3Csup%20class%3D%22fract-num%22%3E1%3C%2Fsup%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22fract-slash%22%3E%2F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22fract-den%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3E%20feet%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E42%3A2b%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3E50%26%23xA0%3Bcubits%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5B26.5%26%23xA0%3Bmeters%5D%3B%20also%20in%2042%3A7%2C%26%23xA0%3B8.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20wide.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_42_3%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EOne%20block%20of%20rooms%20overlooked%20the%2035-foot%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E42%3A3%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3E20%5B-cubit%5D%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5B10.6-meter%5D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20width%20of%20the%20inner%20courtyard.%20Another%20block%20of%20rooms%20looked%20out%20onto%20the%20pavement%20of%20the%20outer%20courtyard.%20The%20two%20blocks%20were%20built%20three%20levels%20high%20and%20stood%20across%20from%20each%20other.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_42_4%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EBetween%20the%20two%20blocks%20of%20rooms%20ran%20a%20walkway%2017%3Csup%20class%3D%22fract-num%22%3E1%3C%2Fsup%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22fract-slash%22%3E%2F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22fract-den%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3E%20feet%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E42%3A4a%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3E10%26%23xA0%3Bcubits%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5B5.3%26%23xA0%3Bmeters%5D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20wide.%20It%20extended%20the%20entire%20175%26%23xA0%3Bfeet%20of%20the%20complex%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E42%3A4b%3C%2Fspan%3E%20As%20in%20Greek%20and%20Syriac%20versions%2C%20which%20read%20%3Cem%3EIts%20length%20was%20100%26%23xA0%3Bcubits%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5B53%26%23xA0%3Bmeters%5D%3B%20Hebrew%20reads%20%3Cem%3Eand%20a%20passage%201%26%23xA0%3Bcubit%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5B21%26%23xA0%3Binches%20or%2053%26%23xA0%3Bcentimeters%5D%20%3Cem%3Ewide.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20all%20the%20doors%20faced%20north.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_42_5%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EEach%20of%20the%20two%20upper%20levels%20of%20rooms%20was%20narrower%20than%20the%20one%20beneath%20it%20because%20the%20upper%20levels%20had%20to%20allow%20space%20for%20walkways%20in%20front%20of%20them.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_42_6%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3ESince%20there%20were%20three%20levels%20and%20they%20did%20not%20have%20supporting%20columns%20as%20in%20the%20courtyards%2C%20each%20of%20the%20upper%20levels%20was%20set%20back%20from%20the%20level%20beneath%20it.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_42_7%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EThere%20was%20an%20outer%20wall%20that%20separated%20the%20rooms%20from%20the%20outer%20courtyard%3B%20it%20was%2087%3Csup%20class%3D%22fract-num%22%3E1%3C%2Fsup%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22fract-slash%22%3E%2F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22fract-den%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3E%20feet%20long.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_42_8%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20wall%20added%20length%20to%20the%20outer%20block%20of%20rooms%2C%20which%20extended%20for%20only%2087%3Csup%20class%3D%22fract-num%22%3E1%3C%2Fsup%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22fract-slash%22%3E%2F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22fract-den%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3E%20feet%2C%20while%20the%20inner%20block%26%23x2014%3Bthe%20rooms%20toward%20the%20Temple%26%23x2014%3Bextended%20for%20175%26%23xA0%3Bfeet.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_42_9%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EThere%20was%20an%20eastern%20entrance%20from%20the%20outer%20courtyard%20to%20these%20rooms.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_42_10%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EOn%20the%20south%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E42%3A10%3C%2Fspan%3E%20As%20in%20Greek%20version%3B%20Hebrew%20reads%20%3Cem%3Eeast.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20side%20of%20the%20Temple%20there%20were%20two%20blocks%20of%20rooms%20just%20south%20of%20the%20inner%20courtyard%20between%20the%20Temple%20and%20the%20outer%20courtyard.%20These%20rooms%20were%20arranged%20just%20like%20the%20rooms%20on%20the%20north.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_42_11%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EThere%20was%20a%20walkway%20between%20the%20two%20blocks%20of%20rooms%20just%20like%20the%20complex%20on%20the%20north%20side%20of%20the%20Temple.%20This%20complex%20of%20rooms%20was%20the%20same%20length%20and%20width%20as%20the%20other%20one%2C%20and%20it%20had%20the%20same%20entrances%20and%20doors.%20The%20dimensions%20of%20each%20were%20identical.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_42_12%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20there%20was%20an%20entrance%20in%20the%20wall%20facing%20the%20doors%20of%20the%20inner%20block%20of%20rooms%2C%20and%20another%20on%20the%20east%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20interior%20walkway.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_42_13%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20man%20told%20me%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BThese%20rooms%20that%20overlook%20the%20Temple%20from%20the%20north%20and%20south%20are%20holy.%20Here%20the%20priests%20who%20offer%20sacrifices%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20will%20eat%20the%20most%20holy%20offerings.%20And%20because%20these%20rooms%20are%20holy%2C%20they%20will%20be%20used%20to%20store%20the%20sacred%20offerings%26%23x2014%3Bthe%20grain%20offerings%2C%20sin%20offerings%2C%20and%20guilt%20offerings.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_42_14%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20the%20priests%20leave%20the%20sanctuary%2C%20they%20must%20not%20go%20directly%20to%20the%20outer%20courtyard.%20They%20must%20first%20take%20off%20the%20clothes%20they%20wore%20while%20ministering%2C%20because%20these%20clothes%20are%20holy.%20They%20must%20put%20on%20other%20clothes%20before%20entering%20the%20parts%20of%20the%20building%20complex%20open%20to%20the%20public.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_42_15%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20the%20man%20had%20finished%20measuring%20the%20inside%20of%20the%20Temple%20area%2C%20he%20led%20me%20out%20through%20the%20east%20gateway%20to%20measure%20the%20entire%20perimeter.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_42_16%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20measured%20the%20east%20side%20with%20his%20measuring%20rod%2C%20and%20it%20was%20875%26%23xA0%3Bfeet%20long.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E42%3A16%3C%2Fspan%3E%20As%20in%2045%3A2%20and%20in%20Greek%20version%20at%2042%3A17%2C%20which%20reads%20%3Cem%3E500%26%23xA0%3Bcubits%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5B265%26%23xA0%3Bmeters%5D%3B%20Hebrew%20reads%20%3Cem%3E500%26%23xA0%3Brods%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5B5%2C250%20feet%20or%201%2C590%20meters%5D%3B%20similarly%20in%2042%3A17%2C%2018%2C%2019%2C%2020.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_42_17%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20he%20measured%20the%20north%20side%2C%20and%20it%20was%20also%20875%26%23xA0%3Bfeet.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_42_18%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20south%20side%20was%20also%20875%26%23xA0%3Bfeet%2C%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_42_19%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3Eand%20the%20west%20side%20was%20also%20875%26%23xA0%3Bfeet.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_42_20%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%2220%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E20%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20the%20area%20was%20875%26%23xA0%3Bfeet%20on%20each%20side%20with%20a%20wall%20all%20around%20it%20to%20separate%20what%20was%20holy%20from%20what%20was%20common.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_43_1%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2243%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EEzekiel%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E43%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22subhead-sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Glory%20Returns%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EAfter%20this%2C%20the%20man%20brought%20me%20back%20around%20to%20the%20east%20gateway.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_43_2%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2243%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3ESuddenly%2C%20the%20glory%20of%20the%20God%20of%20Israel%20appeared%20from%20the%20east.%20The%20sound%20of%20his%20coming%20was%20like%20the%20roar%20of%20rushing%20waters%2C%20and%20the%20whole%20landscape%20shone%20with%20his%20glory.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_43_3%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2243%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20vision%20was%20just%20like%20the%20others%20I%20had%20seen%2C%20first%20by%20the%20Kebar%20River%20and%20then%20when%20he%20came%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%2